config BR2_PACKAGE_QUEST
	bool "quest"
	help
	  QuEST (Quantum Exact Simulation Toolkit) is a high-performance
	  quantum computer simulator with zero external dependencies.

	  Features:
	  - Pure C implementation with C++ wrappers
	  - Zero mandatory dependencies
	  - Supports OpenMP multithreading
	  - Supports MPI distributed computing
	  - Over 140 quantum operations
	  - Configurable numerical precision

	  Ideal for embedded systems due to minimal footprint.

	  https://quest.qtechtheory.org/
